                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180909-139-defend1130 t18180909-139-punish769"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>. Aged 21.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
